Run Game:
    python main_game.py player_balance [ number_of_card_decks ]

Betting options:
1. Double Down: Player can double his initial bet following the initial two-card deal, but can't
double down after splitting.

2. Split Hand: Player can split the initial two-card hand into two and play them separately when
the first two cards are equal value.

3. Soft Hand: Ace can be counted as 1 or 11 to both dealer and player.
